comments: Drummond (DET) establishes his screening path in Ball's (NOP) path and does not deliver contact.
Ingram (NOP) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Brown (DET) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Brown (DET) makes clean contact to the ball while defending Ingram (NOP).
Brown (DET) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Ingram (NOP) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Okafor (NOP) makes contact to Kennard's (DET) body at the end of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Ball (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Rose's (DET) drive to the basket.
Griffin (DET) briefly engages and disengages with Ingram (NOP).
Griffin (DET) places a hand to the front of Ingram (NOP) during the drive, but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Griffin (DET) has his hand rested on Ingram's (NOP) side and removes it as he begins his upward shooting motion.
Rose (DET) releases from Holiday (NOP) at the end of his drive that does not dislodge Holiday from his legally obtained position.
Griffin (DET) briefly grasps Redick's (NOP) arm during the inbound but does not affect his FOM.
